Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python, debconf, python-pygooglechart (>= 0.2), python-matplotlib (>= 0.98), python-gdchart2 (>= 0.beta1-3.4), python-django (>= 1.2.1), python-alogger (>= 2.0), django-placard (>= 1.3.4), django-andsome (>= 1.1.14), django-pbs (>= 1.1.1), django-surveys (>= 1.0.1), django-xmlrpc (>= 0.1), python-django-south (>= 0.7), django-simple-captcha, django-ajax-selects (>= 1.2.3), django-shibboleth (>= 1.1)
Description: Collection of Django apps to manage a cluster
 Features 
 .
  Can store user information and/or posix account information in LDAP
  Admin portal for cluster administrators
  User portal for cluster account holders
  Usage portal, special portal just displaying usage information
  Email notification
  Auto account creation - Allow project leaders to manager their users 
 .
 Modules
 .
  people - Manage people and institutes
  project - Manage projects
  usage - displays usage statistics generated from cluster data
  software - Manage software licenses and agreements
  machines - Manage clusters and cluster user accounts
  projectreports - create surveys for project leaders to fill out 
